How would you fix the monolithic 'Daemon' struct and the 'daemon.go' file to enforce the Single Responsibility Principle (SRP)?
// Original Monolithic Struct:
type Daemon struct {
    id                string
    repository        string
    containers        container.Store // Concern 1: Container Management
    networkManager    network.Manager // Concern 2: Networking
    storageAdapter    storage.Storage // Concern 3: Storage
    // ... 50+ fields handling many concerns
}

